    "body": "As mentioned in issue #332 this adds the possiblity to specify an LD_LIBRARY_PATH in compilers.yaml\n\n```\ngcc@4.4.7:\n    cc  = /usr/bin/gcc\n    cxx = /usr/bin/g++\n    f77 = /usr/bin/gfortran\n    fc  = /usr/bin/gfortran\n    ld_library_path = /what/ever/you/need\n```\n\nIf considered useful, I will clean up and document. \n",
